    "en": {
      "title": "3-hour power cut from 3rd - 5th - Public Utilities Commission",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has published the list of power cuts in the country from tomorrow 3rd to 5th.",
        "Accordingly, power cut has been implemented for 3 hours in the next three days.",
        "In \"ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW\" the power cut will be enforced for one hour and 40 minutes during day time and one hour and 20 minutes at night.",
        "2 hours 30 minutes power cut will be enforced in CC section from 6.00 am to 8.30 am.",
        "It is also noted that power cut will be enforced for 3 hours from 5.30 am to 8.30 am in the sections \"MNOXYZ\"."
      ],
